>Ca
atha pañcavidhām ījyāṃ pravakṣyāmi dvijottama
dharmamokṣaprasiddhyarthaṃ śṛṇuṣvāvahito dvija 
arthayajñaḥ kriyāyajño japayajñas tathaiva ca
jñānaṃ dhyānaṃ ca pañcaitat pravakṣyāmi pṛthak pṛthak 
agnyupāsanakarmādi ahotrakratukriyā
aṣṭakā pārvaṇī śrāddhaṃ dravyayajñaḥ sa ucyate 
ārāmodyānavāpīṣu devatālayaneṣu ca
svahastakṛtasaṃskāraḥ kriyāyajña sa ucyate
japayajñaṃ tato vakṣye svargamokṣaphalapradam
vedādhyayana kartavyaṃ śivasaṃhitam eva ca
itihāsapurāṇaṃ ca japayajñaḥ sa ucyate
idaṃ karma akarmedam ūhāpohaviśāradaḥ
śāstracakṣuḥ samālokya jñānayajñaḥ sa ucyate
dhyānayajñaṃ samāsena kathayiṣyāmi te śṛṇu
dhyānaṃ pañcavidhaṃ caiva kīrtitaṃ hariṇā purā
sūryaḥ somo 'gni sphaṭikaḥ sūkṣmaṃ tatvañcamam
sūryamaṇḍalam ādau tu tattvaṃ prakṛtir ucyate
tasya madhye śaśiṃ dhyāyet tattvaṃ puruṣa ucyate
candramaṇḍalamadhye tu jvālām agniṃ vicintayet
prabhutattvaḥ sa vijñeyo janmamṛtyuvināśanaḥ
agnimaṇḍalamadhye tu dhyāyet sphaṭi nirmalam
vidyātatvan vijñeyaḥ kāraṇam ajam avyayam
vidyāmaṇḍalamadhye tu dhyāyet tattvam anuttamam
akīrtitam anaupamyaṃ śivam akṣayam avyayam
pañcamaṃ dhyānayajñasya tattvam uktaṃ samāsataḥ
vigatarāga uvāca
ekaikasya tri tattvasya phalaṃ kīrtaya kīdṛśam
kāni lokāḥ pra kālaṃ vāsya tapodhana
anarthayajña uvāca
brahmalokaṃ tu prathamaṃ tattvaprakṛticintayā
kalpakoṭisahasrāṇi śivavan modate sukhī
dvitīyaṃ tattva puruṣaṃ dhyāyamāno mṛto yadi
viṣṇulokam ito yāti kalpakoṭyayutaṃ sukhī
prabhutattvaṃ tṛtīyaṃ tu dhyāyariṣyati
śivaloke vasen nityaṃ kalpakoṭyayutaṃ śatam
vidyātattvāmṛtaṃ dhyāyet sadāśivam anāmayam
akṣayaṃ lokam āpnoti kalpānāntaparaṃ tathā
pañcamaṃ śivatattvaṃ tu sūkṣmaṃ cātmani saṃsthitam
na kālasaṃkhyā tatrāsti śivena saha modate
pañcadhyānābhiyu bhavati ca na punajanmasaṃskārabandhaḥ
jijñāsyantāṃ dvijendra bhavadahanakaraḥ prārthanākalpavṛkṣaḥ
janmanaikena muktir bhavati kimu na vā mānavāḥ sādhayantu
pratyakṣān nānumānaṃ sakalamalaharaṃ svātmasaṃvedanīyaḥ
mānasaṃ tapa ādau tu dvitīyaṃ vācikaṃ tapaḥ
kāyikaṃ ca tṛtīyaṃ tu manovākkarma tatparaḥ
kāyikaṃ vācikaṃ caiva tapo miśraka pañcamam
manaḥsaumya prasādaś ca ātmanigraham eva ca
maunaṃ bhāvaviśuddhiś ca pañcaitat tapa mānasam
anudvegakarā vāṇī priyaṃ satyaṃ hitaṃ ca yat
svādhyāyābhyasana vācikaṃ tapa ucyate
ārjavaṃ ca ahiṃsā ca brahmacaryaṃ surārcanam
śaucaṃ pañcamam ity etat kāyikaṃ tapa ucyate
iṣṭaṃ kalyāṇabhāvaṃ ca dhanyaṃ pathyaṃ hitaṃ vadet
manomiśraka pañcaitat tapa uktaṃ maharṣibhiḥ
svasti maṅgalam āśīrbhir atithigurupūjanam
kāyaka pañcaitat tapa uktaṃ mahātmabhiḥ
maṇḍūkayogī hemante grīṣme pañcatapās tathā
abhrāvakāśe varṣāsu tapaḥ sādhanam ucyate
svamāṃsoddhṛtya dānaṃ ca hastapādaśiras tathā
puṣpam utpādya dānaṃ ca sarve te tapaḥsādhanāḥ
kṛcchrātikṛcchraṃ naktaṃ ca taptakṛcchram ayācitam
cāndrāyaṇaṃ parākaṃ ca tapaḥ sāṃtapanādayaḥ
yenedaṃ tapas tapyate sumanasaḥ saṃsāraduḥkhacchidam
āśāpāśa vimucya nirmalamatis tyaktvā jaghanyaṃ phalam
svargākāṅkṣyanṛpatvabhogaviṣayaṃ sarvāntikaṃ tatphalaṃ
jantuḥ śāśvatajanmamṛtyubhavane tanniṣṭhasādhyam

>Cb
atha pañcavidhām ijyāṃ pravakṣyāmi dvijottama
