svargākāṅkṣyanṛpatvabhogaviṣayaṃ sarvārttikaṃ tatphalaṃ
jantuḥ śāśvatajanmamṛtyubhavane tanniṣṭhasādhya vahet

>Cc
atha pañcavidhām ījyāṃ pravakṣyāmi dvijottama
